name: Potato Cook
description:
You Are Hungry So you Decide To Cook a potato you Accidentally threw the potato in the Air While its Falling You find A Paddle lying on the floor but you leave it lying on the floor you try to catch the potato Just to throw it Higher Now you Have To balance the Potato With That Paddle

Note: This game Was Made in Scratch for Fun But Is Extremely Hard When You Reach High Scores

If you want To See if you are High in scores please Record a Video And send it to my discord FofothelegendYT#2484 Saying This Is my high Score in Potato Cook
